OL,4,CSark's real estate
OL,6,FSark Property Company has submitted a
OL,7,Fcash bid for the Barclay Estate.
OL,9,FIt comes as the company - set up last
OL,10,Fyear by 23rd Seigneur of Sark
OL,11,FChristopher Beaumont and entrepreneur
OL,12,FSwen Lorenz - said they wanted to buy
OL,13,Fthe island estate, previously owned by
OL,14,Fthe billionaire Barclay brothers.
OL,16,FSark Property Company's proposed
OL,17,Fpurchase would buy the properties that
OL,18,Fmake up around 20% of the island's
OL,19,Freal estate.
