OL,3,CCash bid submitted to purchase 20% of
OL,4,CSark's real estate
OL,6,FThis includes 80 residential
OL,7,Fdwellings, 20 commercial properties,
OL,8,Ffour hotels, and 139 acres of land.
OL,10,FA trust of the late Sir David Barclay,
OL,11,Fwho died in 2021, currently owns the
OL,12,FSark estate.
OL,14,FWhile an exact figure has not been
OL,15,Fprovided, Sark Property Company
OL,16,Fbelieves their offer reflects the
OL,17,F"market value for the estate" as well
OL,18,Fas a premium.
