OL,3,CCash bid submitted to purchase 20% of
OL,4,CSark's real estate
OL,6,FKnight Frank, the current owner's
OL,7,Fadvisor, has confirmed that the
OL,8,Fcompany's bid will be passed on to the
OL,9,Ftrustees of Sir David Barclay's estate
OL,10,Ffor their consideration.
OL,12,FChristopher Beaumont, Director of the
OL,13,FSark Property Company, says: "It's
OL,14,Ftaken a lot of work to get to the
OL,15,Fpoint of submitting a bid, but that
OL,16,Ftime and effort has been well spent
OL,17,Fbuilding an investment proposition
OL,18,Fthat would give Sark a better future.
