OL,4,CSark's real estate
OL,6,F"Our bid is backed by cash, our
OL,7,Finvestment case is solid, and our
OL,8,Fintention is to create the right
OL,9,Fenvironment for Sark to thrive."
OL,11,FThe bid hopes to help Sark with its
OL,12,Fhousing shortages, financial
OL,13,Fchallenges, and insufficient
OL,14,Ffacilities following the closure of
OL,15,Fseveral hospitality outlets in 2014 in
OL,16,Fprotest at how the island was governed.
