OL,6,FSark Property Company also say that
OL,7,Fthe transaction will be subject to the
OL,8,Fisland's Property Transfer Tax of
OL,9,F7.5%, meaning Sark would see an
OL,10,Fimmediate cash boost,
OL,12,FThe company's CEO, Swen Lorenz says
OL,13,Fthe offer is only valid for 30 days.
OL,15,FHe explains: "Even though there can be
OL,16,Fno guarantee that a transaction will
OL,17,Ftake place, we are confident that our
OL,18,Fbid will make for a compelling
OL,19,Fproposition.
